Don-
I did use roofing flash but it is too thin, ended up with sharp edges  
and tears.  In the end the roofing flash will be part of it but I  
will need the flexible material for a good seal.  Metal all the way  
across will be very noisy, transferring noise and vibration to the body.
John I.

